OL,3,CWindrush victims to get new funding
OL,4,Cand commissioner, government announces
OL,6,FVictims of the Windrush scandal will
OL,7,Freceive new financial support to help
OL,8,Fwith compensation claims, along with a
OL,9,Fspecific Windrush Commissioner, the
OL,10,Fgovernment announced on Wednesday.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,13,Fthere will be a "fundamental reset" in
OL,14,Fthe government's response to the
OL,15,Fscandal, announcing #1.5 million of
OL,16,Fnew government funding to better
OL,17,Fsupport victims with compensation
OL,18,Fclaims.
