OL,3,CWindrush victims to get new funding
OL,4,Cand commissioner, government announces
OL,6,FAlongside this, there will be a
OL,7,FWindrush Commissioner appointed, and a
OL,8,Fspecific Home Office Unit responsible
OL,9,Ffor Windrush.
OL,11,FThe Windrush scandal saw people who
OL,12,Fhad legally arrived in the UK from the
OL,13,FCarribean after 1948 threatened with
OL,14,Fdeportation and detention. Those
OL,15,Faffected also lost access to housing,
OL,16,Fhealthcare, bank accounts, and driving
OL,17,Flicences.
