OL,4,Cand commissioner, government announces
OL,6,FThe government eventually acknowledged
OL,7,Fits mistakes and established a
OL,8,Fcompensation scheme, but many people
OL,9,Fhave been wrongly denied compensation,
OL,10,Fand more than 50 people have died
OL,11,Fbefore receiving any compensation.
OL,13,FCooper said: "The Windrush scandal
OL,14,Fcaused terrible pain and heartache for
OL,15,Fso many families in the Windrush
OL,16,Fgeneration and in wider Commonwealth
OL,17,Fcommunities. It is rightly recognised
OL,18,Fas a period of national shame.
