OL,3,CWindrush victims to get new funding
OL,4,Cand commissioner, government announces
OL,6,F"We are changing the government's
OL,7,Fapproach ` working more closely with
OL,8,Fvictims, stakeholders, and
OL,9,Fcommunities, as well as those affected
OL,10,Fby all the department's work, to
OL,11,Fensure a scandal of this kind can
OL,12,Fnever happen again and dignity can be
OL,13,Frestored to those so tragically
OL,14,Faffected."
OL,16,FA 2020 report put the blame on the
OL,17,FHome Office for the scandal, saying it
OL,18,Fwas "foreseeable and avoidable" and
OL,19,Fvictims were let down by "systemic
OL,20,Foperational failings" at the
OL,21,Fdepartment.
