OL,6,FStarmer is at the Commonwealth Heads
OL,7,Fof Government Meeting in Samoa, where
OL,8,FCarribean leaders are asking the UK to
OL,9,Fengage with discussions around
OL,10,Freparatory justice for the UK's role
OL,11,Fin the slave trade.
OL,13,FBut the PM says he's only focused on
OL,14,Fthe "future" rather than the "past",
OL,15,Fand any conversation about reparations
OL,16,Fwould lead to "very long endless
OL,17,Fdiscussions".
