OL,6,FBut one of his ministers signaled a
OL,7,Fshift in position on Thursday, saying:
OL,8,F"We're not opposed to having a
OL,9,Fconversation about any of the issues
OL,10,FCommonwealth heads of government want
OL,11,Fto raise".
OL,13,FThe Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy did
OL,14,Fhowever reiterate that "our focus is
OL,15,Fnot on reparations".
OL,17,FThe prime minister said his focus at
OL,18,Fthe summit is on other issues like
OL,19,Fclimate, which he believes is among
OL,20,Fthe most important concerns for the
OL,21,Fother countries.
